Package: pdn-bbs
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: Tom Fanning <tom@m0lte.uk>
Recommends: packetnet
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/m0lte/pdn-bbs
Description: Packet-radio BBS app package for the Packet.NET node (pdn)
 A ground-up packet-radio mailbox — personal mail, bulletins and NTS traffic
 with FBB-compatible store-and-forward and webmail. Ships as a Packet.NET app
 PACKAGE: pdn discovers it under /usr/share/packetnet/apps/bbs and the node
 owner enables it from the control panel. Self-contained: bundles its own .NET
 runtime, so no system runtime is required. Inert without the packetnet node
 host (hence the soft Recommends), but installable standalone.
